umap-rstr
=========

This product is a derivative work: a Clojure port, built on the raster
typed-dispatch compiler, of UMAP (Uniform Manifold Approximation and
Projection).

The original algorithm and its reference implementation, umap-learn, are:

    Copyright (c) 2017, Leland McInnes
    https://github.com/lmcinnes/umap
    BSD 3-Clause License

McInnes, L., Healy, J., & Melville, J. (2018). UMAP: Uniform Manifold
Approximation and Projection for Dimension Reduction. arXiv:1802.03426.

The Clojure / raster port in this repository is:

    Copyright (c) 2026, Christian Weilbach

and is released under the same BSD 3-Clause License (see LICENSE). It is an
independent reimplementation that follows umap-learn's algorithm and numerical
behaviour; it is not endorsed by or affiliated with the original authors.
